= SDL_SetHint =
Use this function to set a hint with normal priority.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_bool SDL_SetHint(const char* name,
                     const char* value)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''name'''
|the hint to set; see the list of Hints on [http://wiki.libsdl.org/moin.cgi/CategoryHints#Hints CategoryHints] for details
|-
|'''value'''
|the value of the hint variable; see the individual Hint for details
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns SDL_TRUE if the hint was set, SDL_FALSE otherwise.

